sentences.sentence: She propped herself up on one elbow.
Investments in the U.S. money market have propped up the American dollar.
sentences.translation: 对美国货币市场的投资一直在支撑着美元。

sentences.sentence: Sam slouched back and propped his elbows up on the bench behind him.
sentences.translation: 萨姆懒懒地往后一靠，将他的两胳膊肘撑在了他背后的长凳上。
